":"Remove Varoma tray. Slice omelette into thin strips then add strips and prawns to bowl with noodles. Stir to combine.","step":11},{"isHeader":false,"content":"Top Pad Thai with bean sprouts, chives, reserved coriander leaves, shallots and reserved chopped peanuts. Serve immediately with lime wedges on the side.","step":12}],"usefulItems":"baking paper, large serving bowl","id":"r146843","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-vXGr3fNVTD8\/XZMyNSomSUI\/AAAAAAAAah4\/DdIkZCQ__ok_ACO_UAFiztshRMcWqIoTgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_6xLc5lDDTJCV5SGv.png","title":"Pad Thai Noodles with Prawns","ingredients":[{"isHeader":true,"content":"Ingredients"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"200 g dried rice noodles, flat, medium"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"water, boiling, for soaking"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"80 g roasted peanuts, unsalted,"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"3 garlic cloves"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 fresh red chilli, deseeded if desired"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"6 sprigs fresh coriander, roots and stems, reserving leaves for garnishing"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"20 g olive oil, plus extra for greasing"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 ½ Tbsp fish sauce"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"40 g lime juice (approx. 2-3 limes)"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 Tbsp tamarind paste"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"2 Tbsp soy sauce"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"¼ tsp shrimp paste"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"3 tsp palm sugar (approx. 1 cm cube), grated"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"2 medium eggs"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"500 g water"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"350 g raw prawns, peeled"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"70 g fresh bean sprouts, for garnishing"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"10 fresh chives, finely chopped, for garnishing"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"3 Tbsp crispy, fried shallots, for garnishing"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 lime, cut in wedges, for serving"}],"nutrition":["per 1 portion","1480 kJ \/ 352 kcal","29 g","17.3 g","17.5 g"],"hints